/span>&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190820/59954420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F59954420&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41C8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=12b8b30c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190820%2F59954420&h=5ab88955\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190820/59954420</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T14:07:08.000Z","msg":"自首因為唔好令警察難做，鐵心支持警察嘛，但問題係一開始點解要除衫著草呢？自己報警拉自己吖嘛，浪費警力"}]}